<xml xmlns="https://developers.google.com/blockly/xml">
  <variables></variables>
  <block type="add_view" id="main_view" x="100" y="100">
    <field name="NAME">OpenAI API Demo</field>
    <next>
      <block type="ui_heading" id="title">
        <field name="LEVEL">1</field>
        <field name="TEXT">ü§ñ OpenAI API Integration Demo</field>
        <next>
          <block type="ui_alert" id="api_key_notice">
            <field name="TYPE">warning</field>
            <field name="TEXT">üîë This demo requires OpenAI API key. Replace 'YOUR_OPENAI_KEY' in code with your actual API key from https://openai.com/api/</field>
            <next>
              <block type="ui_paragraph" id="intro">
                <field name="TEXT">Explore the power of AI with OpenAI's GPT models, embeddings, and image generation. Activate the OpenAI module first!</field>
                <next>
                  <block type="ui_card" id="chat_card">
                    <field name="TITLE">üí¨ Chat Completion</field>
                    <next>
                      <block type="ui_paragraph" id="chat_desc">
                        <field name="TEXT">Generate AI responses using ChatGPT:</field>
                        <next>
                          <block type="openai_openai_chat" id="chat_demo">
                            <value name="MODEL">
                              <block type="text" id="model_text">
                                <field name="TEXT">gpt-3.5-turbo</field>
                              </block>
                            </value>
                            <value name="MESSAGES">
                              <block type="json_array" id="messages_array">
                                <statement name="ITEMS">
                                  <block type="json_property" id="message_obj">
                                    <value name="KEY">
                                      <block type="text" id="role_key">
                                        <field name="TEXT">role</field>
                                      </block>
                                    </value>
                                    <value name="VALUE">
                                      <block type="text" id="role_value">
                                        <field name="TEXT">user</field>
                                      </block>
                                    </value>
                                    <next>
                                      <block type="json_property" id="content_prop">
                                        <value name="KEY">
                                          <block type="text" id="content_key">
                                            <field name="TEXT">content</field>
                                          </block>
                                        </value>
                                        <value name="VALUE">
                                          <block type="text" id="content_value">
                                            <field name="TEXT">Explain quantum computing in simple terms</field>
                                          </block>
                                        </value>
                                      </block>
                                    </next>
                                  </block>
                                </statement>
                              </block>
                            </value>
                            <value name="MAX_TOKENS">
                              <block type="math_number" id="max_tokens">
                                <field name="NUM">150</field>
                              </block>
                            </value>
                            <next>
                              <block type="ui_divider" id="div1">
                                <next>
                                  <block type="ui_card" id="embeddings_card">
                                    <field name="TITLE">üîç Text Embeddings</field>
                                    <next>
                                      <block type="ui_paragraph" id="embeddings_desc">
                                        <field name="TEXT">Convert text to numerical vectors for semantic search:</field>
                                        <next>
                                          <block type="openai_openai_embeddings" id="embeddings_demo">
                                            <value name="INPUT">
                                              <block type="text" id="embedding_text">
                                                <field name="TEXT">Artificial intelligence and machine learning</field>
                                              </block>
                                            </value>
                                            <next>
                                              <block type="ui_divider" id="div2">
                                                <next>
                                                  <block type="ui_card" id="usage_card">
                                                    <field name="TITLE">üìö Usage Guide</field>
                                                    <next>
                                                      <block type="ui_code" id="usage_guide">
                                                        <field name="LANG">markdown</field>
                                                        <field name="CODE"># OpenAI API Usage

## Setup Steps:
1. **Get API Key**: Visit https://openai.com/api/
2. **Create Account**: Sign up and get your API key
3. **Set Budget**: Configure usage limits to avoid surprises
4. **Replace Token**: Update 'YOUR_OPENAI_KEY' in generated code

## API Models:
- **GPT-3.5-Turbo**: Fast, cost-effective chat
- **GPT-4**: More capable, higher cost
- **text-embedding-ada-002**: Text embeddings
- **DALL-E**: Image generation

## Best Practices:
- Cache responses to save costs
- Use appropriate max_tokens limits
- Implement error handling
- Monitor usage and costs

## Cost Estimates:
- GPT-3.5-Turbo: ~$0.002/1K tokens
- GPT-4: ~$0.03/1K tokens
- Embeddings: ~$0.0001/1K tokens</field>
                                                      </block>
                                                    </next>
                                                  </block>
                                                </next>
                                              </block>
                                            </next>
                                          </block>
                                        </next>
                                      </block>
                                    </next>
                                  </block>
                                </next>
                              </block>
                            </next>
                          </block>
                        </next>
                      </block>
                    </next>
                  </block>
                </next>
              </block>
            </next>
          </block>
        </next>
      </block>
    </next>
  </block>
